<center>
<h1><font color="#883EBA">Welcome to the Word Count Machine!</font></h1>
<h3>You can use this handy machine to count the number of times a specific word appears in a sentence.</h3>
<h3>Once you enter your sentence and the word you would like counted, make sure to hit <font color="#2f96b4">COUNT</font> to see your results!</h3>
</center>
<br>
<form action="/count">
  <div class="form-group">
     <label for="compare">Please enter a sentence.</label>
     <input id="compare" name="compare" class="form-control" type="text" required>
  </div>
  <div class="form-group">
     <label for="word">What word would you like to count?</label>
     <input id="word" name="word" class="form-control" type="text" pattern="[a-zA-Z]+" title="include only one word with no spaces" required>
  </div>
  <center><button type="submit" class="btn-info">COUNT</button></center>
</form>
